Question: One image has only two, blue dumbells and the other image has dumbbells of multiple colors.

Reference Answer: False

Left image URL: https://i.ebayimg.com/00/s/NzY4WDEwMjQ=/z/tVwAAOSwSypY92Wj/$_86.JPG

Right image URL: http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-AMTRpoKmVNs/VU0sEQmgPOI/AAAAAAAAHdw/mJ-9BmuS2tk/s1600/IMG_0068.JPG

Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many blue dumbells are in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many blue dumbells are in the image?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Are there dumbells of multiple colors?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Are there dumbells of multiple colors?')
ANSWER4=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} == 2 and not {ANSWER2}')
ANSWER5=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} == 2 and not {ANSWER3}')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER4} xor {ANSWER5}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER6)
```
